title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
description: The getcolumnlabel method is not returning user recognizable strings when accessing column labels from the metadata object.
OB: The getcolumnlabel method is not returning any values for column labels when accessed from the metadata object.
EB: The getcolumnlabel method should return user recognizable strings for column labels when accessed from the metadata object.
SR:
1. Open the application.
2. Access the metadata object.
3. Call the getcolumnlabel method to retrieve column labels.
4. Verify that the method returns user recognizable strings for the column labels.
